[{"id":776318,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1620106885","description":"<p>LZ 目前某 985 大三在读，现在是已经拿到了 BAT 三家的实习 offer，岗位都挺满意，如果选择工作的话估计就通过实习转正的途径       </p>\n<p>学习成绩还行，保研本校没啥问题，正式开始申请应该在 9 月初      </p>\n<p>目前想直接工作，一是担心读研 3 年出来就业形势更加严峻，二是自己本身也对做算法不太感兴趣，读研出来大概率还是找研发岗的工作       </p>\n<p>但是又比较纠结，担心学历贬值，本科学历会成为以后职业发展，晋升这些的短板(还有 35 岁以后找退路的选择也非常有限?)     </p>\n<p>纠结 ing，看看各位有没有什么建议</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776318","replies":116,"created_ts":1620733698,"created":"19:48:18","title":"985 大三 工作 or 保研？","author":"drperry","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/drperry","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d7798dfa1f16565844d29c23677d7c5?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776306,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1620107083","description":"<p>目前家里放了一台服务器，兼做了 NAS 的一些功能，但是现在就是担心文件的安全性，怕硬盘突然损坏，所以想找一个靠谱的云存储平台（因为某些限制条件，不能组 raid，同时组 raid 在我看来也并非万无一失）。</p>\n<p>有三点需求，\n一是需要大容量（至少 5T，因为目前我的文件都已经 3T 多了），\n二是希望不是国内的平台（海边玩耍的视频变成了教育短片，实在是心理阴影），\n三是最好 Linux Server 可以直接操作的（毕竟服务器无 GUI ）</p>\n<p>接受付费！接受付费！接受付费！（预算 2000/年）</p>\n<p>谢谢大家</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776306","replies":101,"created_ts":1620728286,"created":"18:18:06","title":"请问一下大家，有没有靠谱的云存储平台推荐一下？","author":"mateor95","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mateor95","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/de73b9c9efd474415a08cbf7123cedb1?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776138,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1618915561","description":"<p><img alt=\"WX20210511-083320.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/05/11/QhFCOtBADIvy7rE.png\"/></p>\n<p>👉 <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/id1555383303\" rel=\"nofollow\">下载链接</a></p>\n<h2>介绍</h2>\n<p>※ 完全根据艾宾浩斯遗忘曲线规律打造，用科学的方法帮助用户巩固单词记忆</p>\n<p>※ 内置丰富词库，满足不同学习需要，包含：四六级、雅思、托福、GRE 、专四、专八、考研词汇，后续会扩充更多</p>\n<p>※ 灵活制定复习计划，可自行选择词库，单词数量，一切就绪后， [简记] 会聪明地帮你自动生成一份复习计划表，你所需要做的就是按照计划表执行即可</p>\n<p>※ 内置单词发音和系统自带词典查询</p>\n<h2>兑换码（兑换后希望在评论告知一下序号，没了我会在 append 区域补上）</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>KJRRLJA6RRPX  </li>\n<li>7WKNJ7KYKAL7  </li>\n<li>AYT6TRHKTENM  </li>\n<li>RY667AHFHJT9  </li>\n<li>JPLLNTTNH6F3  </li>\n<li>K4KWJ463NF43  </li>\n<li>7HFX7YF4JNLT  </li>\n<li>E6NFEPNPAMRW  </li>\n<li>97AMXHNFM6L6  </li>\n<li>XJWWNA7PYJLR  </li>\n<li>M7A3XNHETWYX  </li>\n<li>RJYXNNMMNYAT  </li>\n<li>L94J4AJ9R36N  </li>\n<li>33WEMLF9Y4K9  </li>\n<li>E6RW37MKM4JY  </li>\n<li>9TPHW7PR3N6W  </li>\n<li>AWJME6NP7A96  </li>\n<li>A7PE7X74J6KE  </li>\n<li>TXXHRWE4PHT6  </li>\n<li>KMMRY7RRMMPR</li>\n</ol>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776138","replies":82,"created_ts":1620693861,"created":"08:44:21","title":"送码｜简记单词 新鲜上线，艾宾浩斯背单词应用，在背单词或准备背单词的小伙伴不妨试试","author":"AlwaysBee","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AlwaysBee","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/738d/2477/113573_mini.png?m=1499820409"},{"id":776302,"node":"奇思妙想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1595507885","description":"打算搞个电子消费品（或者说智能家电）品牌，产品可能是智能饮水机、电子测温枪、智能运动手环等生活类电子消费品，但是去注册商标（ 9 、11 、12 类）发现太难了，想了几十个都通不过。求助各位，给点建议取个名字，2 个字最好，最好中英文都有，听上去比较有科技感、00 后喜欢的未来感的，能体现“电子智能产品是人体一部分”这样的理念的。<br /><br />多谢各位啦！","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776302","replies":71,"created_ts":1620727250,"created":"18:00:50","title":"各位高手，求一个电子消费品牌的商标名称，采纳可行送 500 元红包","author":"oott","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oott","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/80a76e293e942e3b81d74f9c11f68095?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776201,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1620107083","description":"<p>这些东西无益于赌博，赌狗你们知道是什么下场吗，即使赚钱了也有一天亏回去，萌新还是老老实实上班别想赚横财</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776201","replies":71,"created_ts":1620704495,"created":"11:41:35","title":"给各位提醒一下千万不要买炒各种虚拟币","author":"Mr0C","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Mr0C","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2b309674ae5734b4458b7753ae33b0db?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776276,"node":"旅行","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/travel","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc22/1309/181_mini.png?m=1608240651","description":"五一去了趟舟山嵊泗列岛，完美避开节日人流，岛上生活很安逸，吃住都不算便宜，总体体验还是很棒的。<br />关于嵊泗列岛:虽然名义上归舟山管辖，但实际上从上海出发最近，到本岛船程一个半小时。<br />路线:上海-嵊泗本岛-花鸟岛-枸杞岛-上海。<br />推荐花鸟岛和枸杞岛:<br />花鸟岛全岛都是 ins 风，各种文艺的民宿和小店，哪怕是什么都不做只在岛上发发呆也好。缺点吃住偏贵，需要额外支付 85 元上岛费。<br />枸杞岛和嵊山岛通过一座桥连接，风景不错，在海上牧场看日落很美，嵊山岛的无人村已经开发成景点，镇上生活相对方便。<br /><br />小插曲:因为每天的船次只有一辆班，并且随时有可能因为风浪停航，所以上岛要有滞留在岛上的准备。好在每程我都买到了船票，转岛的那天都恰好开航。<br /><br />直接上图:<br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ug1tw51j20zk0noack.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ug27j9gj21900u00vc.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ug4c51ij22wo26ie83.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ug6nl1vj22fp1tshdu.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ug8sbvdj22xq27anpf.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ugcabghj23342bce84.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ugi0ucrj23342bc7wj.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> <br /><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/5f18ebd8ly1gq7ugl8q5tj22v225bu10.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"> ","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776276","replies":67,"created_ts":1620721390,"created":"16:23:10","title":"嵊泗列岛归来~真·人少景美，节假日没有人从众","author":"ichigo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ichigo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b4bf/5de1/17661_mini.png?m=1387335720"},{"id":776154,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","description":"<p>我看一些人说国区只有几百万或者接近千万首吧，但是也有人说现在曲库有 6000w 。有点糊涂了，哪位大佬能科普一下..</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/gUlEGj\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"gUlEGj.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/05/11/gUlEGj.jpg\"/></a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776154","replies":62,"created_ts":1620698269,"created":"09:57:49","title":"Apple music 现在国区和外区的曲库差别大吗？","author":"Lunatic1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lunatic1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9a50/6600/378941_mini.png?m=1595841875"},{"id":776307,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>工作以后有一个发现，越来越丧失对生活的感知力，感觉做什么都提不起劲。</p>\n<p>好像处在前有堵截后有追兵而又无法突围的困境中一样。</p>\n<p>每天都会担心自己和家庭的未来，无时无刻不在为自己的前景焦虑。</p>\n<p>自己和朋友的交集也越来越少，有时候心里有事想找个朋友一吐为快，翻开通讯录找了半天最后还是放弃了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776307","replies":60,"created_ts":1620728507,"created":"18:21:47","title":"如何突围一潭死水一样的人生","author":"chogath","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chogath","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9051/0dd1/506037_mini.png?m=1620802531"},{"id":776179,"node":"English","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/en","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/57ae/ee35/229_mini.png?m=1448883313","description":"<p>本人英语特别差（属于那种看到英语文基本上是文盲的那种，但是专业内的单词还是懂的），每次看文档还得靠翻译软件，想在这一年学习下英语，找不到从零开始学习路径，去报班，但是每天时间就那么点，没法挤出时间去报班，想就在网上学。\n我在想买现在初高的教材跟着学效果会怎么样？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776179","replies":56,"created_ts":1620701207,"created":"10:46:47","title":"如何学习英语","author":"TiggeYL","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/TiggeYL","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9709be2ab8219063c213d4eb39560760?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776161,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1620106885","description":"<p>老板技术出身，我负责技术，发现很多技术细节，老板出现了干涉的情况。有时候具体到数据库怎么设计，字段怎么命名。<br/>\n每个人有自己的设计思路，以及业务实现方式。<br/>\n有时候感觉老板在强加自己的意志于我，搞得我很没自主性。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776161","replies":56,"created_ts":1620699528,"created":"10:18:48","title":"碰到一个技术出身的老板怎么办？","author":"jackerbauer","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jackerbauer","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b31d/7645/536249_mini.png?m=1614995706"},{"id":776187,"node":"买买买","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mmm","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/dc56/8979/804_mini.png?m=1406296248","description":"<p>习惯性会把外包装存起来，以便后续方便转手，但是最近一年购入的东西有点多，房间里也占了不小的位置，请问大家有没有比较好的处理方式？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776187","replies":54,"created_ts":1620702303,"created":"11:05:03","title":"大家会留着各种东西的包装吗？","author":"Eins","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Eins","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5294/73f2/122732_mini.png?m=1434520389"},{"id":776285,"node":"DevOps","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/devops","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3871/bd64/622_mini.png?m=1585380634","description":"<p>需求\n1 、敲一条命令， 这条命令能够分发到所有已经打开的窗口</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776285","replies":49,"created_ts":1620723687,"created":"17:01:27","title":"推荐一款 ssh 终端","author":"blueorange","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/blueorange","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4e0999ebbb206f06d76dd25508f39beb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":776147,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"<p>我是二手房的买方，没有经验，疑问如题。除了找担保公司这条路，我该尽量如何规避风险？这个合同怎么签？希望有类似经验的朋友给点建议。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776147","replies":46,"created_ts":1620696473,"created":"09:27:53","title":"卖方需要用到买方的首付款去解押房产证，我是买方。","author":"laohelmet","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/laohelmet","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b6b2/3a0b/453785_mini.png?m=1576263911"},{"id":776326,"node":"深圳","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1598508742","description":"看到小米的\"吃到饱卡\"的套餐资费不错，就想办张用，支持联通和电信两个运营商，不过听说深圳的联通信号很糟糕？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776326","replies":40,"created_ts":1620735717,"created":"20:21:57","title":"深圳有兄弟是联通卡吗？想问问手机信号如何。","author":"Suigintou","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Suigintou","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/19ed/bd4f/525038_mini.png?m=1613785274"},{"id":776213,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"<p>卫生间比较小，没办法做干湿分离</p>\n<p>装修的时候，也没注意这个问题，没用防滑地砖，导致现在洗澡后地面很滑，家里有小朋友，已经摔了几次了</p>\n<h2>目前的方案有：</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>加垫子：很容易藏污纳垢，老婆觉得难看</li>\n<li>用手钻电磨在地砖上面搞十字纹路，有朋友这样做，但是实际效果也有限，同样容易藏污纳垢不好清理，不清理防滑效果也会下降</li>\n<li>淘宝上的防滑剂，个人对这个报怀疑的态度，没其它方案的话，后面应该会尝试一下</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>问：</h2>\n<p>V 友们有没有比较好的解决方案？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776213","replies":40,"created_ts":1620708956,"created":"12:55:56","title":"卫生间如何防滑","author":"Ansen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Ansen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d481/fbe5/13344_mini.png?m=1585299139"},{"id":776338,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"<p>最近又确诊颈椎曲度变直，坐久了就脖子痛，脑袋也昏昏沉沉的，有时候觉得走路都不稳，完全无法集中精力，做事情晕乎乎的。想到未来还有那么长的时间，感觉有点绝望。请了两天假，但是过了这两天，还是要去面对生活。自己大把的时光都在医院门诊度过，饮食运动也要各种注意和禁忌，想不明白为啥过的比同龄人艰难和灰暗，觉得真的很难过。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/776338","replies":36,"created_ts":1620740255,"created":"21:37:35","title":"年纪轻轻，身体一堆毛病，唉","author":"AichiB7A","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/AichiB7A","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f7974807d7e46d9e781d608034e51202?s=24&d=retro"}]